1
00:01:10,752 --> 00:01:12,431
=Those Days=

2
00:01:12,431 --> 00:01:14,800
(Adapted from iceread.com novel
"You Xi" by Qingyang Wanxi)

3
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:17,980
=Episode 33=

4
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:42,380
(Nanzhou New District People's Court.)
(Sealed)

5
00:01:57,839 --> 00:01:59,000
Why are you here?

6
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,440
I came to bring you something.

7
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,800
Keep your voice down.

8
00:02:04,048 --> 00:02:04,960
Keep your voice down.

9
00:02:06,119 --> 00:02:06,919
Let me do it.

10
00:02:06,919 --> 00:02:08,200
Come, I'll change my shoes.

11
00:02:08,559 --> 00:02:09,559
Go sit.

12
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,200
What's wrong?

13
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,599
Mingzhu fell asleep.

14
00:02:13,999 --> 00:02:14,879
She's asleep?

15
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,399
What's wrong with her?

16
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:18,960
Nothing.

17
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:21,480
Mom, why are you here?

18
00:02:22,839 --> 00:02:24,240
Why can't I come?

19
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:26,750
It's my daughter's home.
I have to report to you before coming?

20
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:28,520
Come, sit.

21
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,040
Come.

22
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,920
Come, sit.

23
00:02:32,279 --> 00:02:32,879
Well...

24
00:02:33,839 --> 00:02:34,559
Are you okay?

25
00:02:34,559 --> 00:02:35,159
I'm fine.

26
00:02:35,220 --> 00:02:36,960
Don't busy yourself.
Mrs. Feng, I'll do it.

27
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,879
Sit down, it's fine.

28
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,200
Let my Mother-in-law do it.

29
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,599
She needs more exercise,
which helps her recovery.

30
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,719
Here, have some water.

31
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:46,320
Wow, not bad.

32
00:02:47,559 --> 00:02:49,119
I've recovered very well.

33
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:50,999
I exercise every day.

34
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:55,040
Mingzhu and Meiqi
also take good care of me.

35
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,760
Where's Meiqi?

36
00:02:57,770 --> 00:02:59,550
She went to the hospital
to get my medicine.

37
00:03:00,770 --> 00:03:01,439
Have some water.

38
00:03:01,679 --> 00:03:02,240
Okay.

39
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:04,279
Wait.

40
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:06,999
Minghui made seafood porridge.

41
00:03:07,279 --> 00:03:07,879
Really?

42
00:03:08,599 --> 00:03:09,520
I'll serve you some.

43
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:09,999
Okay.

44
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:15,439
Minghui is such a good kid.

45
00:03:16,679 --> 00:03:17,279
Yes.

46
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:19,159
I was wrong in the past.

47
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:20,599
Why bring that up?

48
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:21,879
It's all in the past.

49
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,240
And we're all one family now.

50
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:24,599
Here.

51
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,719
Minghui was immature before.

52
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,480
Naughty, mischievous.

53
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,520
But now he can stand on his own.

54
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,800
Smells so good.

55
00:03:36,915 --> 00:03:38,240
He cooked it for quite a while.

56
00:03:41,999 --> 00:03:42,839
Drink slowly.

57
00:03:42,839 --> 00:03:43,599
Okay.

58
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,640
Here, Mingzhu, you drink first.

59
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,679
Mom, you drink first.

60
00:03:46,839 --> 00:03:48,559
You drink first. I'll serve her.

61
00:03:49,559 --> 00:03:50,080
Here.

62
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:50,999
Here.

63
00:03:52,839 --> 00:03:53,480
Okay.

64
00:03:59,839 --> 00:04:00,679
Thank you, Mom.

65
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:03,159
It might be hot. Drink slowly.

66
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:03,679
Okay.

67
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:08,920
It's good.

68
00:04:09,582 --> 00:04:10,520
- Right?
- It's nice.

69
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,080
It's good.

70
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:21,359
Mom.

71
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,599
I bought you some fruit.

72
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:29,080
Remember to eat it.

73
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,239
Zhidong left.

74
00:04:40,719 --> 00:04:41,279
Mom.

75
00:04:42,719 --> 00:04:44,000
What you just said,

76
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:46,640
together with that expression of yours,

77
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:50,404
anyone who didn't know would think
something happened to my brother.

78
00:04:50,599 --> 00:04:52,640
Xu Zhidong and Bichen

79
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:55,159
flew away together happily
as a couple, okay?

80
00:05:01,479 --> 00:05:03,320
Zhixia.

81
00:05:04,239 --> 00:05:06,440
My little sweetheart.

82
00:05:08,159 --> 00:05:08,880
Really.

83
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:11,839
Take a portion

84
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:13,120
of these wontons with you later.

85
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:15,080
And bring another portion
to your sister.

86
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,120
By the way,

87
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,640
how's your sister doing lately?

88
00:05:19,839 --> 00:05:20,919
Not great.

89
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,279
Why?

90
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:25,120
She's heavily pregnant,

91
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,520
with a stroke-stricken Mother-in-law
at home,

92
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,880
an unemployed sister-in-law,

93
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,239
and a pile of debt.

94
00:05:31,359 --> 00:05:32,279
What do you think?

95
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,440
She's in deep trouble.

96
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:34,719
No.

97
00:05:34,719 --> 00:05:37,359
Help her! Give her a hand!

98
00:05:37,359 --> 00:05:38,520
What about...

99
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,640
Her useless mother?

100
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,382
What is she doing?
Why isn't she helping?

101
00:05:41,493 --> 00:05:43,120
Mom, what you said is not right.

102
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,919
What do you mean "useless mother"?

103
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:45,789
I...

104
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:47,360
She was the one who wiped poop and pee

105
00:05:47,370 --> 00:05:48,150
and raised Mingzhu.

106
00:05:48,150 --> 00:05:49,626
She's also the one running around

107
00:05:49,648 --> 00:05:51,137
helping Mingzhu through hard times.

108
00:05:51,248 --> 00:05:53,204
How did she become "useless"
in your mouth?

109
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:55,520
Who exactly is useless,
and who is the real one?

110
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:57,880
How can you talk like that?

111
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,919
I didn't know your sister's situation.

112
00:05:59,919 --> 00:06:01,279
Now that I know, what?

113
00:06:01,279 --> 00:06:02,760
Haven't I given money and effort?

114
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,560
Wasn't that big bracelet bought by me?

115
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,120
Mom.

116
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,799
We know you treat Mingzhu well.

117
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,604
But no matter how well,

118
00:06:09,648 --> 00:06:11,440
you're just making up for the past,
right?

119
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,399
But the "useless mother" you said

120
00:06:13,399 --> 00:06:14,799
is the one who truly gave.

121
00:06:14,799 --> 00:06:17,120
She gave for over 20 years,
every single day.

122
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:20,839
Xu Zhixia.

123
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,279
Why is your elbow

124
00:06:23,279 --> 00:06:25,279
always pointing outward?

125
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,359
You know clearly.

126
00:06:27,359 --> 00:06:28,839
Your grandmother gave the child away.

127
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,640
I didn't know at the time!

128
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,200
You can't use every little thing

129
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:34,000
to provoke me like this.

130
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,239
In your opinion, why does

131
00:06:35,239 --> 00:06:36,839
that Yue Xiu'e become a fairy?

132
00:06:37,599 --> 00:06:38,880
She's a scammer!

133
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,320
She's a bandit!

134
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,919
She took my child away

135
00:06:41,919 --> 00:06:42,960
and then ran off!

136
00:06:44,599 --> 00:06:46,239
If you talk like that, I won't be happy.

137
00:06:46,479 --> 00:06:48,359
How am I "turning my elbow outward"?

138
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,159
I'm just telling the truth, okay?

139
00:06:51,710 --> 00:06:52,715
If there's anything,

140
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,230
can't we sit down and talk calmly?

141
00:06:54,239 --> 00:06:56,159
I already argue nonstop
with Zhang Hao at home.

142
00:06:56,159 --> 00:06:58,159
I don't want to come here
and argue with you.

143
00:06:58,919 --> 00:07:00,719
Mingzhu is tired. Me too.

144
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,919
Am I not your biological daughter?

145
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,239
Alright, you...

146
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,680
Come here, Zhixia.

147
00:07:11,039 --> 00:07:11,560
I...

148
00:07:12,799 --> 00:07:15,719
You came all the way to argue with me.

149
00:07:16,239 --> 00:07:16,760
I...

150
00:07:19,359 --> 00:07:21,520
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

151
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,359
Mom.

152
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:26,000
What I mean is...

153
00:07:27,399 --> 00:07:29,520
Let the past stay in the past.

154
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,080
Alright?

155
00:07:30,479 --> 00:07:33,159
Let's stop bringing up old issues.

156
00:07:33,479 --> 00:07:34,880
No matter who's right or wrong,

157
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,839
no matter who's "real" or "fake",

158
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:38,239
none of that matters.

159
00:07:38,239 --> 00:07:39,399
It's all in the past, okay?

160
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,440
Right now,

161
00:07:40,599 --> 00:07:42,200
if we have money, time, or energy,

162
00:07:42,359 --> 00:07:44,159
we should help Mingzhu however we can.

163
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,640
Mingzhu is having a hard time.

164
00:07:45,719 --> 00:07:46,680
Maybe soon

165
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,039
she won't even have a job.

166
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,440
Morning, Mr. Zhao.

167
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,640
Mingzhu.

168
00:07:58,693 --> 00:08:00,560
I already told you,
there's nothing I can do.

169
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,604
Why did you come again?

170
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:03,680
Look.

171
00:08:03,919 --> 00:08:05,760
These are freshly steamed
Jinling meat buns.

172
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:06,560
They're delicious!

173
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,159
Try one.

174
00:08:07,159 --> 00:08:09,200
I queued for so long to buy them.

175
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:10,640
Right now,

176
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,320
even if you brought me
Jinling meat buns

177
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,599
or even human-flesh char siu buns,

178
00:08:14,599 --> 00:08:16,210
I still can't arrange
a position for you.

179
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:17,520
You must have a way.

180
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,440
Please help me think again.

181
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,159
How can I stay?

182
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,000
There's no way.

183
00:08:24,479 --> 00:08:25,799
Not even a little?

184
00:08:26,479 --> 00:08:27,120
None.

185
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,159
Unless you really have the ability

186
00:08:31,239 --> 00:08:32,800
to take over the entire F&B department

187
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:33,839
of our hotel.

188
00:08:34,359 --> 00:08:35,560
If you really can do it well,

189
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:37,200
you'd earn way more than working here.

190
00:08:40,060 --> 00:08:41,720
What are the requirements
to contract it?

191
00:08:41,737 --> 00:08:43,182
Annual payment of 300,000 yuan.

192
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,839
Paid in advance.

193
00:08:48,599 --> 00:08:50,239
How's it? 300,000 yuan.

194
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,680
Do you have it?

195
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,800
I don't even have 30,000 yuan.

196
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,960
So,

197
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,999
just stay home and rest.

198
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,639
You're a girl.

199
00:09:00,839 --> 00:09:01,759
Why make life so hard?

200
00:09:01,848 --> 00:09:02,990
I'm going out for a while.

201
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,639
Thanks for the buns.

202
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:08,048
I just happened to skip breakfast.

203
00:09:08,093 --> 00:09:09,226
Sit here yourself.

204
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,440
Mom.

205
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,280
This is a new skill I learned.

206
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,200
You know, just this process alone

207
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,599
costs 280 yuan for a single session
at the rehab center.

208
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,440
So I'm saving money.

209
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,359
Exactly.

210
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,599
Meiqi.

211
00:09:25,719 --> 00:09:26,999
I have been dragging you down.

212
00:09:28,999 --> 00:09:30,680
So you need to get better quickly.

213
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,719
Yes, I'll try hard.

214
00:09:32,719 --> 00:09:34,680
Look at me, I can do this...

215
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,040
I'll do this for you every day.

216
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:36,920
I'm back.

217
00:09:37,239 --> 00:09:38,200
Mingzhu is back.

218
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,582
- Mingzhu.
- Rest for a while.

219
00:09:39,719 --> 00:09:40,680
How is it, Mingzhu?

220
00:09:42,719 --> 00:09:44,479
There's some unrealistic good news.

221
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,071
The F&B department

222
00:09:46,071 --> 00:09:48,115
of Nanxi Hotel might let me
take the contract.

223
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,719
But...

224
00:09:50,479 --> 00:09:51,719
It costs 300,000 yuan a year.

225
00:09:56,119 --> 00:09:57,280
Indeed unrealistic.

226
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,479
Mingzhu is just cheering us up.

227
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:00,800
Here I come.

228
00:10:01,839 --> 00:10:03,080
- Mrs. Feng is here.
- Auntie.

229
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,080
Mom, why did you come again?

230
00:10:05,115 --> 00:10:06,590
A restaurant can't be left unattended.

231
00:10:06,848 --> 00:10:08,750
Why would you say that?
Your dad's not a person?

232
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:10,071
Your brother's not a person?

233
00:10:10,599 --> 00:10:11,560
Give it to me.

234
00:10:12,359 --> 00:10:13,680
I saw a super fresh

235
00:10:13,839 --> 00:10:15,839
free-range chicken

236
00:10:15,839 --> 00:10:16,839
at the market today.

237
00:10:16,839 --> 00:10:18,280
I'd come cook it for you.

238
00:10:18,599 --> 00:10:19,920
Thanks, Mrs. Shen.

239
00:10:19,982 --> 00:10:20,680
Thanks for what?

240
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:22,920
You're all weak and recovering.
You need to eat well.

241
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:24,280
Recover sooner.

242
00:10:24,599 --> 00:10:26,320
Okay, thank you.

243
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,160
Mom, put it there.

244
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:29,359
Put it down. I'll do it.

245
00:10:29,359 --> 00:10:31,040
- Don't touch it.
- I'll handle it myself.

246
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,080
You're just making a mess.

247
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,960
Go rest.

248
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,719
You're not helping. Hurry.

249
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,119
Mrs. Shen.

250
00:10:36,671 --> 00:10:37,800
Thank you for your hard work.

251
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,040
Stop saying that.

252
00:10:39,239 --> 00:10:40,440
If you're worried about me,

253
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:42,119
then recover quickly.

254
00:10:42,119 --> 00:10:43,560
Later I'll teach you and you can cook.

255
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:44,239
I won't learn.

256
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,680
It tastes better when you cook.

257
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:47,879
You're lazy.

258
00:10:50,100 --> 00:10:53,159
(Xin City Grand Court)

259
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:53,879
Here, right?

260
00:10:54,119 --> 00:10:54,719
Yes.

261
00:10:55,599 --> 00:10:57,800
When have I ever walked this far?

262
00:10:58,639 --> 00:10:59,400
Young man,

263
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,719
open the door for me.

264
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,479
Auntie, who are you looking for?

265
00:11:02,719 --> 00:11:03,839
I'm looking for Shen Mingzhu.

266
00:11:03,999 --> 00:11:04,879
I'm her mother.

267
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:06,320
I'm her father.

268
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:09,999
How many Moms are there?

269
00:11:09,999 --> 00:11:11,160
Don't worry about that.

270
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,320
I'm her real mom.

271
00:11:12,359 --> 00:11:13,519
Open the door.

272
00:11:13,999 --> 00:11:14,639
Mrs. Feng.

273
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,960
Be careful when chopping
the chicken later.

274
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,040
Our kitchen knife

275
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,709
isn't very good. Don't cut your hand.

276
00:11:19,710 --> 00:11:21,137
- Don't worry.
- Who is it?

277
00:11:21,137 --> 00:11:21,604
I...

278
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,719
I'll go.

279
00:11:23,582 --> 00:11:24,920
- Did you order food?
- Coming!

280
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:25,719
No.

281
00:11:27,999 --> 00:11:29,359
Uncle, Auntie.

282
00:11:29,359 --> 00:11:30,040
You...

