00:11:30,599 --> 00:11:31,920
We came to see Mingzhu.

284
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:33,839
Come in.

285
00:11:33,839 --> 00:11:34,320
Mingzhu.

286
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:34,960
Okay, come in.

287
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,359
The security downstairs
swipes the card for us.

288
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,359
Mingzhu.

289
00:11:40,060 --> 00:11:41,404
- We can't...
- Why are you here?

290
00:11:41,404 --> 00:11:42,750
