00:11:48,239 --> 00:11:49,759
This is my mother-in-law.

295
00:11:50,719 --> 00:11:51,560
Hello, Mrs. Feng.

296
00:11:51,759 --> 00:11:52,680
Hello.

297
00:11:53,239 --> 00:11:54,599
Um, excuse me.

298
00:11:54,599 --> 00:11:55,719
My leg...

299
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,080
No, don't get up.

300
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,599
You sit.

301
00:11:57,599 --> 00:11:58,680
Sit.

302
00:11:58,680 --> 00:11:59,719
