307
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:10,680
I fart really well.

308
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:15,999
Fart really well.

309
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:18,480
That's because of strong lungs.

310
00:12:18,490 --> 00:12:20,479
Yes, the healthier you are,
