311
00:12:20,479 --> 00:12:21,280
Yes.

312
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:21,759
Right.

313
00:12:22,119 --> 00:12:24,200
Alright, Mrs. Shen.
Stop busying yourself.

314
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:24,680
