a few months,

605
00:23:49,239 --> 00:23:50,799
you won't really suffer any loss.

606
00:23:51,120 --> 00:23:52,600
At least you'll be left

607
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:54,471
with a restaurant ready
to operate anytime.

608
00:23:54,719 --> 00:23:55,479
What do you think?

609
00:23:57,239 --> 00:23:58,440
What you said is all true.

610
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:00,719
I can also understand how you feel.

611
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:03,279
But the risks involved

612
00:24:03,719 --> 00:24:05,200
