613
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:09,880
Mr. Zhao.

614
00:24:11,279 --> 00:24:12,759
I studied marketing.

615
00:24:12,999 --> 00:24:14,160
I made a model.

616
00:24:15,239 --> 00:24:17,279
According to our operational concept,

617
00:24:17,279 --> 00:24:18,759
basically, by the seventh month,

618
00:24:18,759 --> 00:24:20,759
