I'll help you negotiate
with the higher-ups.

631
00:24:55,079 --> 00:24:56,719
Alright, thank you, Mr. Zhao.

632
00:24:56,719 --> 00:24:57,360
No problem.

633
00:24:57,360 --> 00:24:58,937
Next time, you treat others to a meal,

634
00:24:58,982 --> 00:24:59,960
