buying materials
and replacing equipment, at least

644
00:25:23,039 --> 00:25:23,799
200,000 yuan.

645
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:26,079
Almost 300,000 yuan in total.

646
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:27,319
About right.

647
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:30,759
