659
00:25:56,271 --> 00:25:58,160
This way, we can take over
the F&B department

660
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,079
of Nanxi Hotel.

661
00:25:59,519 --> 00:26:00,759
Once we do well,

662
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:02,640
