670
00:26:21,479 --> 00:26:22,479
If we don't do well,

671
00:26:23,319 --> 00:26:24,519
then you go out to work.

672
00:26:25,039 --> 00:26:26,719
I'll stay home to take care of everyone.

673
00:26:27,230 --> 00:26:30,071
I don't believe we can starve.

