684
00:27:20,479 --> 00:27:21,039
Hello.

685
00:27:21,239 --> 00:27:22,160
Why are you here?

686
00:27:22,279 --> 00:27:22,759
You...

687
00:27:23,039 --> 00:27:23,759
Please come in.

688
00:27:23,759 --> 00:27:24,360
You go ahead.

689
00:27:24,360 --> 00:27:25,039
Come, please.

690
00:27:25,039 --> 00:27:25,880
Thank you.

691
00:27:26,559 --> 00:27:27,479
- Here.
- Okay.

692
00:27:27,519 --> 00:27:28,550
Come, please sit.

693
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:29,360
