714
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:38,479
Yes.

715
00:28:38,479 --> 00:28:38,960
Here.

716
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:39,600
Sorry.

717
00:28:39,600 --> 00:28:41,640
It's fine. I'll add more
water for you. Here.

718
00:28:42,039 --> 00:28:43,200
- Drink more water.
- Thanks.

719
00:28:43,279 --> 00:28:43,840
It's nothing.

720
00:28:49,920 --> 00:28:51,759
