848
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:50,799
I trust. I do.

849
00:33:51,719 --> 00:33:52,479
Ms. Shen.

850
00:33:53,039 --> 00:33:54,319
You mentioned renovation?

851
00:33:55,079 --> 00:33:56,519
I can handle renovation.

852
00:33:57,559 --> 00:33:59,759
Building materials are my specialty.

853
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:02,039
We can calculate costs properly.

854
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:03,840
At least give me a chance.

855
00:34:03,937 --> 00:34:06,382
If I contract it, it'll definitely
be cheaper than outside.

856
00:34:07,479 --> 00:34:08,440
Yes.

857
00:34:08,937 --> 00:34:09,960
- Alright.
- Thank you.

858
00:34:10,119 --> 00:34:10,920
Don't say like that.

859
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,280
Don't say thanks, Mrs. Feng.

860
00:34:17,479 --> 00:34:18,599
Your house

861
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,280
(On urgent sale)
is listed way too cheap.

862
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:23,880
In a rush to sell.
I need money to pay debts.

863
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,337
I can't list it too high.

864
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,679
Well, your house is so good.

865
00:34:28,679 --> 00:34:30,559
Used such good materials
in the renovation.

866
00:34:30,559 --> 00:34:31,960
Once sold, it can't be bought back.

867
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:34,400
What if we don't sell?

868
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:36,119
The family owes a ton of debt.

869
00:34:36,248 --> 00:34:37,670
My mother-in-law's medical bills

870
00:34:37,679 --> 00:34:39,440
are now nearly 2,000 yuan a month.

871
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,079
Money is needed everywhere.

872
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:42,599
Every day I dream

873
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,599
about filling the holes.

874
00:34:45,826 --> 00:34:47,070
And now the whole neighborhood

875
00:34:47,079 --> 00:34:48,440
knows our situation.

876
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:51,479
I'm worried buyers will check

877
00:34:51,599 --> 00:34:52,920
and think this house is unlucky.

878
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:54,248
In the end, it couldn't be sold.

879
00:35:06,679 --> 00:35:07,679
Then sell it to me.

880
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:13,960
Your marital house
and wedding decor suit me.

881
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:16,400
Hu Gang and I are getting married
very soon.

882
00:35:17,519 --> 00:35:18,159
No.

883
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,679
You don't think this house is unlucky?

884
00:35:21,199 --> 00:35:22,800
What would I be superstitious about?

885
00:35:22,804 --> 00:35:23,880
Look at my Dad's portrait.

886
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:25,639
It's been on my wall
for more than ten years.

887
00:35:25,639 --> 00:35:27,469
And my dad's still lively.

888
00:35:27,470 --> 00:35:29,271
After remarrying,
he even had a successor.

889
00:35:29,315 --> 00:35:31,160
The Ni family doesn't care
about these things.

890
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,679
Don't be too touched.

891
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,119
Give me a discount.

892
00:35:37,119 --> 00:35:38,199
Round off the small change.

893
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:39,559
Anyway,

894
00:35:39,559 --> 00:35:41,440
I'm always a bag holder
for the Feng family.

895
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:48,880
Don't eat? Have some.

896
00:35:49,679 --> 00:35:50,320
Eat.

897
00:36:01,199 --> 00:36:01,960
Mr. Guan.

898
00:36:02,199 --> 00:36:03,159
I didn't expect

899
00:36:03,159 --> 00:36:04,679
your team to be so professional.

900
00:36:05,119 --> 00:36:06,840
Please don't be polite, Mr. Shen.

901
00:36:06,999 --> 00:36:07,840
I'm not being polite.

902
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,199
I just came to learn.

903
00:36:09,199 --> 00:36:10,880
You know,
I know nothing about renovation

904
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:11,840
at all.

905
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:13,679
Don't worry, I'll put in my best effort.

906
00:36:14,999 --> 00:36:15,679
Go ahead.

907
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,039
Mr. Guan.

908
00:36:20,039 --> 00:36:21,559
Dad, why are you here so early?

909
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:24,199
I came to learn.

910
00:36:24,199 --> 00:36:25,400
Now with renovation,

911
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:26,999
I have to learn properly from Mr. Guan.

912
00:36:27,079 --> 00:36:28,199
Mr. Shen, Mr. Guan.

913
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:28,840
Hello.

914
00:36:29,119 --> 00:36:30,840
Mr. Guan, for this renovation,

915
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:32,626
water and electricity
are the top priority.

916
00:36:32,648 --> 00:36:33,071
Alright.

917
00:36:33,079 --> 00:36:34,920
For the wiring, let's use Siping brand.

918
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,679
Good quality, lasts long.

919
00:36:37,519 --> 00:36:38,400
I think

920
00:36:38,599 --> 00:36:40,840
the kitchen needs high power, use 4.0.

921
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:43,119
But 2.5 is enough for the foyer.

922
00:36:43,119 --> 00:36:44,479
This saves money.

923
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,559
Meiqi,

924
00:36:45,720 --> 00:36:47,599
now you finally know how to save money.

925
00:36:49,159 --> 00:36:49,840
Yes.

926
00:37:01,199 --> 00:37:01,920
Jiao.

927
00:37:02,519 --> 00:37:03,199
Mom.

928
00:37:03,893 --> 00:37:05,470
(Nanzhou Shengli Primary School)
Ms. Shen, sorry.

929
00:37:05,479 --> 00:37:06,320
It's okay.

930
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:07,320
Jiao, your mom is here.

931
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:08,320
Thanks, bye.

932
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,119
- Bye.
- Bye.

933
00:37:10,079 --> 00:37:11,159
Were you anxious, Jiao?

934
00:37:11,479 --> 00:37:12,199
Not at all.

935
00:37:13,199 --> 00:37:14,639
How did you do in math today?

936
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:15,679
Not well.

937
00:37:16,479 --> 00:37:17,039
Mom.

938
00:37:17,039 --> 00:37:18,320
What's for dinner tonight?

939
00:37:18,320 --> 00:37:20,360
If you didn't do well,
what's there to eat?

940
00:37:21,159 --> 00:37:23,479
People are iron, and food is steel.

941
00:37:23,479 --> 00:37:25,240
If you skip a meal, you get starving.

942
00:37:26,679 --> 00:37:27,960
Alright, no time to cook.

943
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:29,599
Go to your dad's workplace
for a meal.

944
00:37:30,199 --> 00:37:30,840
Got it.

945
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:31,800
Seat belt.

946
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:39,440
Hao.

947
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,400
Come quickly.

948
00:37:43,079 --> 00:37:43,679
Dad.

949
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,639
Ordered so many dishes?

950
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:47,840
Because I ordered all dishes Jiao loves.

951
00:37:48,519 --> 00:37:49,679
Dad is the best.

952
00:37:49,679 --> 00:37:50,920
Of course I'm the best.

953
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:54,320
Tell your dad how much you scored
in math.

954
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,880
See if he still loves you so much.

955
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,920
Don't want to hear it.
Just don't want to hear this.

956
00:37:57,920 --> 00:37:58,800
Let's eat first.

957
00:37:58,880 --> 00:37:59,519
Exactly.

958
00:38:00,159 --> 00:38:01,479
Just spoil her, okay?

959
00:38:07,639 --> 00:38:08,199
Wu.

960
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:11,960
Can I do the social recruitment

961
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,582
presentation during overtime tonight?

962
00:38:15,199 --> 00:38:16,039
You need it now?

963
00:38:17,150 --> 00:38:18,671
Can't it wait until after dinner?

964
00:38:21,159 --> 00:38:21,800
Well...

965
00:38:22,679 --> 00:38:23,920
My daughter is here.

966
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:25,800
I want to eat with her for a while.

967
00:38:25,999 --> 00:38:27,119
In ten minutes, okay?

968
00:38:29,315 --> 00:38:30,550
Alright, I'll come over now.

969
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:33,880
What presentation?

970
00:38:34,159 --> 00:38:35,240
Urgent presentation?

971
00:38:35,982 --> 00:38:37,880
Actually,
this social recruitment presentation

972
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:38,840
is for next week.

973
00:38:40,039 --> 00:38:40,999
But Wu,

974
00:38:41,626 --> 00:38:43,182
the new boss, is making a strong start,

975
00:38:43,182 --> 00:38:44,360
and wants to assert authority.

976
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:45,999
Scare you as a warning?

977
00:38:45,999 --> 00:38:47,240
What?

978
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:48,639
What am I?

979
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:49,720
Alright, eat quickly.

980
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:50,999
Jiao, eat more.

981
00:38:50,999 --> 00:38:51,599
Okay.

982
00:38:51,599 --> 00:38:52,760
I am going to work.

983
00:38:53,639 --> 00:38:54,199
Hurry and eat.

984
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,119
Eat something before leaving.

985
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:56,960
Spoil him once.

986
00:39:11,599 --> 00:39:12,599
Why so late?

987
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:15,039
Rush hour. The elevator is hard to get.

988
00:39:15,737 --> 00:39:16,960
Ten minutes is not enough?

989
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:17,760
So impatient?

990
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:18,240
Yes.

991
00:39:23,199 --> 00:39:25,199
Zhang Hao,
do you have a problem with me?

992
00:39:27,119 --> 00:39:27,760
Wu.

993
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,679
It's Manager Wu.

994
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,079
Manager Wu.

995
00:39:36,039 --> 00:39:38,720
CTO is a combined role of tech
and management director.

996
00:39:39,079 --> 00:39:41,199
It requires long-term experience.

997
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,199
So I suggest maybe we can

998
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:45,199
extend the age limit to 40.

999
00:39:45,199 --> 00:39:45,960
Forty?

1000
00:39:46,137 --> 00:39:47,982
Our group is like a retirement home?

1001
00:39:48,519 --> 00:39:50,559
How is forty a retirement home?

1002
00:39:50,800 --> 00:39:52,320
I'm almost forty too.

1003
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:54,679
Exactly, because you're forty.

1004
00:39:54,760 --> 00:39:56,159
So that proves people at forty

1005
00:39:56,159 --> 00:39:57,320
are basically useless.

1006
00:39:57,639 --> 00:39:58,880
Full of negative emotions.

1007
00:39:59,039 --> 00:40:00,871
Always late.
How am I supposed to manage?

1008
00:40:00,893 --> 00:40:01,515
No.

1009
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:03,679
Manager Wu.

1010
00:40:03,679 --> 00:40:06,199
I suggest you know when
to stop sometimes, okay?

1011
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,960
Don't use seniority to pressure me.

1012
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:09,199
I don't buy that.

1013
00:40:09,199 --> 00:40:10,320
Then what do you buy?

1014
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:11,599
What are you doing?

1015
00:40:11,720 --> 00:40:12,560
Am I a persimmon?

1016
00:40:12,570 --> 00:40:13,720
Why do you keep pinching me?

1017
00:40:13,720 --> 00:40:15,137
Zhang Hao, if you're not satisfied,

1018
00:40:15,160 --> 00:40:16,400
go ahead and be the manager.

1019
00:40:16,519 --> 00:40:17,679
Do you have the ability?

1020
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:20,999
Dad.

1021
00:40:25,599 --> 00:40:26,840
Jiao, how did you come?

1022
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,720
Mom asked me to bring you dinner.

1023
00:40:32,280 --> 00:40:32,800
Here.

1024
00:40:33,519 --> 00:40:34,240
Okay, got it.

1025
00:40:34,240 --> 00:40:35,400
Go quickly.

1026
00:40:37,039 --> 00:40:37,720
Go quickly.

1027
00:40:41,519 --> 00:40:42,159
Dad.

1028
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:44,039
You're the best.

1029
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:48,720
Of course I know that.

1030
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:56,039
My daughter.

1031
00:40:59,240 --> 00:41:00,400
Have you thought it through?

1032
00:41:01,440 --> 00:41:02,559
Really selling the house?

1033
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:06,280
Mom, the house is already sold.

1034
00:41:06,999 --> 00:41:08,039
Ni took over it.

1035
00:41:09,720 --> 00:41:11,199
What? That fast?

1036
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,519
Then you...

1037
00:41:15,119 --> 00:41:16,360
You sold the house, and you...

1038
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:18,400
Have you thought
about where you'll live?

1039
00:41:18,679 --> 00:41:19,999
We'll rent a place.

1040
00:41:20,639 --> 00:41:21,679
That won't work.

1041
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:24,400
Adults can endure this suffering,

1042
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:26,039
but the kid can't handle that...

1043
00:41:26,119 --> 00:41:27,079
It's okay, Mom.

1044
00:41:27,240 --> 00:41:28,400
Renting is fine.

1045
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:29,400
Don't worry.

1046
00:41:30,479 --> 00:41:32,440
You've got money but nowhere
to spend it, huh?

1047
00:41:36,559 --> 00:41:38,079
I discussed it with your dad.

1048
00:41:39,079 --> 00:41:40,400
If you really sell the house,

1049
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:42,559
you all can just move in here.

1050
00:41:44,479 --> 00:41:45,639
All move in together?

1051
00:41:46,519 --> 00:41:47,519
How can that work?

1052
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:49,039
Absolutely not, Mom.

1053
00:41:49,671 --> 00:41:50,760
This is just making things

1054
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:51,960
difficult for you and my dad.

1055
00:41:52,679 --> 00:41:53,440
Besides,

1056
00:41:53,519 --> 00:41:55,199
so many people and mouths.

1057
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,159
Back and forth,

1058
00:41:56,159 --> 00:41:57,880
any sentence could cause conflict.

1059
00:41:57,999 --> 00:41:58,999
Absolutely not.

1060
00:41:58,999 --> 00:41:59,800
I'm already

1061
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,479
used to your mother-in-law.

1062
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:03,720
In the future, if she really

1063
00:42:03,720 --> 00:42:05,639
annoys me too much, I'll learn from you.

1064
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:07,880
Just treat her as singing.

1065
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:08,720
That won't work.

1066
00:42:09,026 --> 00:42:10,639
Why is this kid so stubborn? Come here.

1067
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:12,119
Come see.

1068
00:42:13,519 --> 00:42:14,119
Come here.

1069
00:42:17,079 --> 00:42:17,679
Come in.

1070
00:42:23,039 --> 00:42:23,999
What's going on?

1071
00:42:24,240 --> 00:42:25,079
Your brother

1072
00:42:26,159 --> 00:42:27,880
knew you were selling the house,

1073
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:29,760
so he cleaned this place up.

1074
00:42:30,679 --> 00:42:31,519
No, he's living...

1075
00:42:31,519 --> 00:42:32,760
How can he live here?

1076
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:33,960
This definitely won't work.

1077
00:42:34,519 --> 00:42:36,119
He's finally being sensible.

1078
00:42:36,119 --> 00:42:37,920
Give him a chance as his sister.

1079
00:42:38,519 --> 00:42:39,720
It's decided then.

1080
00:42:41,599 --> 00:42:42,599
Hurry up.

1081
00:42:42,760 --> 00:42:44,119
Keep eating. Hurry.

1082
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,950
The world is noisy

1083
00:42:57,550 --> 00:42:59,930
Turning around,
it's already a distant view

1084
00:43:01,350 --> 00:43:03,230
Once I didnt know what to do

1085
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:05,310
What to hold quietly

1086
00:43:05,310 --> 00:43:08,260
Like a silent care

1087
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:12,530
Seasons pass by

1088
00:43:12,530 --> 00:43:15,390
Time ticks away

1089
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,790
Seems like I understand a little

1090
00:43:17,790 --> 00:43:19,570
And also let go of some things

1091
00:43:19,570 --> 00:43:24,290
All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth

1092
00:43:24,290 --> 00:43:27,780
A long letter is written down

1093
00:43:27,930 --> 00:43:31,410
Gently spreading love

1094
00:43:31,610 --> 00:43:35,600
To all the forks in fate

1095
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:41,230
Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved
